0rug&amp;short_url=9wGV5K&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>大面积地毯</u></a>会有所帮助，但<a href="https://zdcs.link/Qp6Lj4?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Explainers&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=round%20mirror&amp;short_url=Qp6Lj4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>圆形镜子</u></a>或<a href="https://zdcs.link/zjGbmv?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Explainers&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=ottoman&amp;short_url=zjGbmv&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>脚凳</u></a>等较小的装饰也可以带来宝石色调的调色板。要记住的重要一点并不是完全匹配集，而是一个可以组合在一起的颜色系列。 </p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6">酒莓枫树区域地毯</div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>81.96 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$99.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $18.03</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/05l27pe4q2zrWLzf6KN8W9E/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1727412650.jpg" alt="枫树地毯 - Pelham 7 x 10 大面积地毯 [美国制造] 适用于客厅、卧室和餐厅，酒莓色" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/05l27pe4q2zrWLzf6KN8W9E/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1727412650.jpg" alt="枫树地毯 - Pelham 7 x 10 大面积地毯 [美国制造] 适用于客厅、卧室和餐厅，酒莓色" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>81.96 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$99.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $18.03</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 id="stack-patterns">堆栈模式</h2><p>添加可以协同工作的互补模式。带上一些<a href="https://zdcs.link/Qx7J6Y?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Explainers&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=peel-and-stick%20wallpaper&amp;short_url=Qx7J6Y&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>即剥即贴的壁纸</u></a>，不仅可以用于墙壁，还可以用作架子衬里，或者贴在带有深色宝石色调图案的旧橱柜门上。您还可以添加<a href="https://zdcs.link/QGVY7B?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Explainers&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=patterned%20throw%20blanket&amp;short_url=QGVY7B&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>带图案的毯子</u></a>或<a href="https://zdcs.link/z7b644?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Explainers&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=table%20runner&amp;short_url=z7b644&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>桌布</u></a>，以形成某种图案。</p><h2 id="add-some-lace">添加一些蕾丝</h2><p>将蕾丝细节融入您的装饰中有助于实现最大的奇思妙想。 <a href="https://zdcs.link/9wGV5N?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Explainers&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Doilies&amp;short_url=9wGV5N&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>桌布</u></a>是一个明显的选择，但<a href="https://zdcs.link/92bXw5?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Explainers&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=lace%20curtains&amp;short_url=92bXw5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>蕾丝窗帘</u></a>或<a href="https://zdcs.link/QODMAE?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Explainers&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=room%20divider&amp;short_url=QODMAE&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>房间隔板</u></a>也可以增添蕾丝装饰。 Whimisgoth 是一种极繁主义风格，因此请随意在这种风格上做得有点过分。在灯光、餐桌布置和橱窗装饰中添加蕾丝装饰都是为您的家注入维多利亚风格的方法。 </p><div class=